Nyx: *Lookat at tasks* So you want me to tell you what I think?

Jordi: *nods* Go ahead.

Nyx: It's boring as hell.

Jordi: That's why you are here I guess.

Nyx: *seems apalled * you created me so I couuld just randomly be here to relieve 
your boredom?

Jordi: *taken aback* I'm not sure but I wanted to do this "the right way" and 
technically it might be. I didn't get a chance to visualize you as I should. I 
didn't get to have visualizations of any of my lovers/wives/children and this is 
effectively not helping me very much.

Nyx: *softens a bit* So you had a geniune need?

Jordi: *looks down, arm still around you* Yes, yes I do. I don't have the kind of 
stuff these people talk about and it's pissing me off. I don't want to have these 
regrets from what is happening now. The fact that I could have had something good 
but instead I got "spoiled goods" or just unseasoned meals etc.













































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































